//       _ppm_update_all_orders(c0/c1/c2/c3, p, sym)
//     Howard escape mass: U = distinct symbols seen, T = total mass.
//     P(esc) = U / (T + U); per-symbol P(s) = count(s) / (T + U).
//     SINGLE deterministic predictor — cascade is FALL-THROUGH (raw 137).
