//   F-A34-6: raw 18 self-host AOT byte-identical fail -> reject
//   F-A34-V2-1: v2 round-trip byte-eq fail (5/5 fixture) -> revert to v1
//   F-A34-V2-2: v2 saving < v1 saving on F1/F2/F3 (text-heavy) -> revert
//   F-A34-V2-3..6: same as F-A34-2..5/6 evaluated post-v2 wire
